# Atlassian Defaults

- When working with Confluence, use the `Grafana-Demo` space by default unless the user specifies a different space.
- When working with Jira, use the `GrafanaDev` space/project by default unless the user specifies a different target.
- If an existing link, ticket key, or page reference points to a different space or project, follow the explicit user-provided context instead of these defaults.
